{"tid":1801561,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔犯法零風險]其實大家知唔知你地有權買黃店外賣然後拎入去starbucks坐住慢慢食?","createTime":"2019-12-28T17:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T06:26:40.000Z","uid":66260,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2600082f19cf2cee29e3a228ea6e00b637afbdd6","tid":1801561,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:24:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1129248880749983&amp;set=gm.2978043308874101&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D1129248880749983%26set%3Dgm.2978043308874101%26type%3D3%26theater&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=0edd5ebb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1129248880749983&amp;set=gm.2978043308874101&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好得罪女人，唔好得罪記性好既女人，唔好得罪記性好又會睇新聞既女人。<br />\n<br />\n仲記得幾年前睇過一單新聞，就係話部分商場入面既starbucks都係擁有食物製造廠牌照，而非食肆牌照。換言之，starbucks附近既座位都係商場既公共空間，並非starbucks顧客先可以使用。<br />\n<br />\n所以今日先去咗 #太子 既 #東京街日本料理 買壽司（#黃）同 #珍煮丹（#黃）買黑糖珍珠厚鮮奶 再去隔離始創starbucks附近既座位坐住食🥰🥰<br />\n<br />\n#東京街 既火炙壽司超高質，強推<br />\n#珍煮丹 係我作為珍珠奶茶控 覺得香港飲過最好既黑糖珍珠鮮奶 珍珠好咬 size適中 黑糖同奶比例最好 唔會過甜 就算冬天好凍轉熱飲都好好飲<br />\n<br />\n至於邊間starbucks得食物製造廠牌，可以用下面條link去check：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/licensing/ecsvread_nonrest_food.html?page=1&amp;subType=所有持牌食物製造廠&amp;licenseType=食物製造廠-&amp;name=starbucks&amp;lang=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Flicensing%2Fecsvread_nonrest_food.html%3Fpage%3D1%26subType%3D%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E6%8C%81%E7%89%8C%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E5%BB%A0%26licenseType%3D%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E5%BB%A0-%26name%3Dstarbucks%26lang%3Dzh-hk&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=52bade72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/licensing/ecsvread_nonrest_food.html?page=1&amp;subType=所有持牌食物製造廠&amp;licenseType=食物製造廠-&amp;name=starbucks&amp;lang=zh-hk</a><br />\n<br />\n以下係兩年前傳真社有關starbucks偽裝商場公共空間為食肆既報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/investigation/歷時7個月的報道，始於一杯咖啡/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Finvestigation%2F%E6%AD%B7%E6%99%827%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%9A%84%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%EF%BC%8C%E5%A7%8B%E6%96%BC%E4%B8%80%E6%9D%AF%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1%2F&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=329a5c9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/investigation/歷時7個月的報道，始於一杯咖啡/</a>"},{"pid":"d5d3405679a2fffa563696a67ed1c2bd09eaf3d1","tid":1801561,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:29:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和你shop 升級：熱情香港 好客之道 又點少得你！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801116</a><br />\n</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ab54e4cac27a98200a3e6e02809bb6c1f0513e","tid":1801561,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:36:19.000Z","msg":"諗過買加藤屋入去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈的障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"59db0c6f7f4b455f2dc8bf892a5382c889be34f2","tid":1801561,"uid":120581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:42:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ec3a1460357e90a08f3ff97ca0cd76b631efd071","tid":1801561,"uid":88428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/